com.sri.ai.util.math

Class BigIntegerNumber

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Number
      • com.sri.ai.util.math.BigIntegerNumber
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<BigIntegerNumber>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BigIntegerNumberApproximate, BigIntegerNumberExact

    public abstract class BigIntegerNumber
extends Number
implements Comparable<BigIntegerNumber>
    An alternative base class to java.math.BigInteger that doesn't commit to the representation being exact (i.e. BigInteger) or approximate (i.e. like java.math.BigDecimal). Intended for use internally by Rational.
    Author:
    oreilly
